Assistant Professor of Media Arts and Sciences
Assistant Professor (Joint) of Aeronautics and Astronautics
Office Hours:
Professor Wood holds office hours regularly as a virtual gathering for group discussion. MIT community members may subscribe to the email list for weekly announcements about office hours here:
https://mailman.mit.edu:444/mailman/listinfo/wood_officehours
. If you have follow up questions or you do not have an MIT email address, email Prof Wood’s Assistant, Alessandra Davy-Falconi for information about office hours at
space-enabledadmin@media.mit.edu
.
